<h4>Our Approach</h4>
<p><strong>Declutter. Organize. Maintain.</strong></p>
<ul>
  <li><strong>Declutter:</strong> Together we will work to sort your belongings so you are left with only the items that bring you most value.</li>
  <li><strong>Organize:</strong> We will ensure that all of your possessions have a specific, purposeful home. This reduces the stress and decision making typically associated with “cleaning up”.</li>
  <li><strong>Maintain:</strong> We provide tips and techniques to help you develop systems to maintain your new lifestyle.</li>
</ul><br>
<hr>
<h4>Our Process</h4>
<p><strong>Consultation. Assessment. Transformation</strong></p>
<ul>
  <li><strong>Consultation:</strong> During the phone consultation, we will discuss your organization goals. This will help us determine the scope of the project, such as whether you want to attack a specific areas of your home or the entire place.</li>
  <li><strong>Assessment:</strong> The first 30 minutes of the at-home session will include a tour and assessment of the space. We will discuss the specific approach for the day.</li>
  <li><strong>Transformation:</strong> For the duration of the session, we will collaborate with you on executing our approach to meet your goals, leaving you with a calm and welcoming space to live and work in.</li>
</ul><br>

